author: Inside Edition
description: Gofret is his name and you can catch him riding around his Turkish town strapped to his human on their motorcycle. Since safety comes first, Gofret even has his own little helmet. His human says when he first started taking the cat out on his bike, the trips were short, but when he saw how well Gofret tolerated the sounds of the motor and the wind in his fur the trips got longer. Inside Edition Digital’s Mara Montalbano has more.
title: Cat Dons Helmet To Go On Motorcycle Rides Around Town

author: Inside Edition
description: These very expensive cars were stolen. In 2023, after a $250,000 purple Rolls-Royce was stolen, the owner used his aerial banner business to help recover it. In 2024, a test drive went wrong when a man trying to sell a Porsche was run over by his own car. In 2018, a 1932 car, once owned by famous aviator Amelia Earhart, was returned to its owner after cops say it was stolen. Inside Edition Digital's Andrea Swindall has more.
title: These Very Expensive Cars Were Stolen
